<@U018WC9RM3K> <@U012BUXVC6B> <@U018B1TFE3Y> <@U0135LQT8TB>
Dear, Leadership:
Today a team of freshmen and sophomores Would like to create a PR bot that would be a chair that you can drive.
We are going to take multiple Safety protocols.
1. Limit the max speed to 0.5. (maybe lower)
2. We will make sure that we test without a driver first
3. Create a max weight
4. Test in the hallway to give the robot more room (also Skystone)
5. The driver will be able to leave the robot at all times
6. Only the driver can move the robot
If you want to add something to the list please tell me

I have linked 2 pictures with this one is off the chairs being used
they are 18in by 16.5in. (more info in <#C01190CKNDN|fabrication>) The second is a design plan note some images are outdated because I was planning to use that chair with no back.
Please message me if you have questions or concerns.
Thank you have a good day
